added.title: Bears and the Beanstalk
added.description: The Bears work as short-order cooks in a giant's diner.

added.title: #PowerSurge
added.description: When Supergirl is presumed dead after a battle with Livewire, Kara Danvers decides to reinvent herself with a new look, a new personality, and a new name, Power Girl.

added.title: #ScrambledEggs
added.description: It's egg-xactly what you think: the home economics "Egg-Baby" assignment, where students are paired up and given an egg to "care for" over a weekend. But when tragedy befalls egg after egg, what should be an easy assignment escalates into a madcap romp with super-high stakes!

added.title: #DramaQueen
added.description: Oliver Queen must face off against his greatest rival yet, Mortimer Drake, while Green Arrow also finds himself up against a new foe, The Cavalier.

added.title: #AllyCat Part 1
added.description: When Zee Zatara realizes Lex Luthor has unearthed a magical book with the power to tell the future, the girls reluctantly enlist Catwoman to help them steal it from him before he understands what he has, but it may already be too late.

added.title: #AllyCat Part 2
added.description: When Zee Zatara realizes Lex Luthor has unearthed a magical book with the power to tell the future, the girls reluctantly enlist Catwoman to help them steal it from him before he understands what he has, but it may already be too late.

added.title: What About Cool James?
added.description: Seth wants some attention, but his family's too busy. But when a lucky explosion forces Cool James to stay with him, Seth gets the attention he craves! That is until Seth sees how much his family loves Cool James.

added.title: Dino Club
added.description: Pressured to choose a real job, Seth instead decides to be a dinosaur like Pam! Soon, all the kids follow suit, but cause so much trouble, Fungietown bans dinosaurs! But Pam can't stop being a dinosaur and is thrown in jail!

added.title: Lion-S
added.description: Lion-O and the other ThunderCats are thrilled to meet a brand new Thunderian: Lion-S! She's cool, good at fighting robots and, most importantly, thinks Lion-O and his Sword of Omens are really neat and interesting! Looks like the ThunderCats have a new best friend! Maybe even, a new ThunderCat?????

added.title: Snarf's Day Off
added.description: Hey everyone, it's Snarf's monthly day off! That's right, this episode follows Snarf as he leaves Cats' Lair to get a needed vacation, by transforming into a normal cat and hanging out with a nice old lady on a farm! But his relaxing day is threatened when Snarf and the nice old lady cross paths with Mumm-Ra!

added.title: Mandora's Law
added.description: Tygra creates a bunch of new laws for Third Earth so Mandora can finally arrest the Mutants. Unfortunately the Thundercats are really bad at following their own rules and the Mutants are really good at working around them.

added.title: Thunder Road
added.description: When a crate containing fifty Swords of Omen lands on Third Earth, the ThunderCats rush out in the ThunderTank to find them. Unfortunately The Mutants and Mumm-Ra want those swords too so it's going to be a race to get to them! A wacky race, you might say. We won't say that, but you might.

added.title: Corporate Buyout
added.description: The Cheetara Corp employee retreat gets canceled when Baron Karnon, a mysterious corporate raider, buys them out! Now Cheetara and Jan-Jan must brave the wilds of Third Earth's most dangerous jungles to find the Baron's office and demand a meeting with the man who stole their company!

added.title: The Upply Strike Back!
added.description: Cole and the Upply arrive at the Skull Sorcerer's keep in the hopes of rescuing Lloyd and the other ninja. But in order to do so, Cole will need to retrieve his mother's fabled swords, the Blades of Deliverance, which are hidden somewhere inside the keep!

added.title: The Son of Lilly
added.description: The battle for the fate of Shintaro Mountain concludes!

added.title: Wasted True Potential
added.description: In the wake of the previous season's victory, the ninja have gone soft and Master Wu must remind them of who they truly are.

added.title: Questing For Quests
added.description: Realizing they have gone soft, the ninja search for a quest to reignite their Spinjitzu training. Unfortunately, NINJAGO City is enjoying a period of rare tranquility.

added.title: A Rocky Start
added.description: The ninja have found their quest! Now they just have to get there, which involves a road trip through the Desert of Doom, a region supposedly inhabited by a giant scarab beetle.

added.title: The Trojan Bear
added.description: When Axel opens a subscription gift-box he didn't even order, the team finds their ranks divided by a robotic bear - or Princess SugarSalt in disguise!

added.title: Thirst for Power
added.description: Axel and his toys deploy the Joyride in a "ship" to "ship" battle against Dr. Nautilus, who has punctured a water main to flood the sewers and established himself as "Admiral Nautilus."

added.title: Party On
added.description: As Zoe preps Cleo LeBall's birthday party, Axel and the team run damage control against a jealous crasher - Princess SugarSalt, who has turned the decorations and gifts into instruments of chaos!

added.title: Bringing Up Baby
added.description: Zoe leaves Axel in charge of the school project - watching over an infant simulator doll - but when MadCap brings the doll to life, Axel and the team must stop the baby without damaging it or risk getting a failing grade!

added.title: Stretched Too Thin
added.description: After a new combo-move leaves Masko permanently limp, Axel and the team must help the fallen luchador get his stretch back.

added.title: Subterranean Homesick Blues/Honey Struck
added.description: Subterranean Homesick Blues: The AO return home to learn that no time has passed but they soon discover their knowledge of brawling has gotten years more advanced./Honey Struck: After Strata is sent packing the AO discover that they have picked up a hitchhiker a Panda-like Bakugan who is nothing but sticky trouble.

added.title: Shun Shine/Ronin Son
added.description: Shun Shine: The AO want to evolve their Bakugan like Dan did with Drago but only Shun finds a way by tapping into the energy of the Mind Core Cell./Ronin Son: When Shun's cousin Masato Kazami claims Hydorous as his intellectual property the AO must battle to keep their friend by their side.

added.title: Framing Device/Bad Actors
added.description: Framing Device: When confronted by China Riot Lia learns to evolve Pegatrix after realizing the true meaning behind her filming obsession./Bad Actors: Dan tries to lie about evolving Drago and gets exposed while the team face off against Duran Dane and his unhappy Bakugan Nillious.

added.title: Tripped Up/Power Tripp
added.description: Tripped Up: Dan and Wynton stumble on both a possible hidden location of the Mind Core Cell and Colonel Tripp who wants the energy source for himself./Power Tripp: After a falling out with Dan, Wynton is mind-controlled by Tripp who stages an attack to ignite a war between Brawlers and the Military.

added.title: A Real Steal/Lightning Unleashed
added.description: A Real Steal: Dan embarks on a solo adventure to outdo Magnus's new team of Bakugan Brawlers and winds up having to be saved by them instead./Lightning Unleashed: Lightning uncovers the Mind Core Cell buried beneath the Earth and battles Stata the Hunter in an effort to protect its secret.

added.title: Los de Arriba Contra Atacan
added.description: Cole y los de abajo llegan para rescatar a los Ninjas. Para ello, Cole tendrá que recuperar las espadas legendarias, las Espadas de la Liberación.

added.title: El Hijo de Lilly
added.description: iLa batalla por el destino de la Montaña Shintaro concluye!

added.title: Potencial Desperdiciado
added.description: A raíz de la victoria de la temporada anterior, los ninjas se han ablandado y el Maestro Wu debe recordarles quiénes son realmente.

added.title: Buscando Misiones
added.description: Al darse cuenta de que se han ablandado, el ninja busca una misión para reactivar su entrenamiento de Spinjitzu. Desafortunadamente, la ciudad de NINJAGO está disfrutando de un período de rara tranquilidad.

added.title: Un Comienzo Dificil
added.description: iLos ninja han encontrado su búsqueda! Ahora solo tienen que llegar allí, lo que implica un viaje por carretera a través del desierto de Doom, una región supuestamente habitada por un escarabajo gigante.

added.title: #SobrecargaElectrica
added.description: Cuando creen que Supergirl ha muerto en una batalla con Livewire, Kara Danvers decide reinventarse con una nueva apariencia, una nueva personalidad y un nuevo nombre: iPower Girl!
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: #HuevosRevueltos
added.description: Gracias a la tarea de la clase de Economía Domestica, los estudiantes son emparejados y se les entrega un huevo para "cuidar" durante el fin de semana. Pero cuando la tragedia acontece huevo tras huevo, lo que debería ser una tarea fácil, ise convierte en una disparatada persecución!
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: #LaReinaDelDrama
added.description: Oliver Queen debe enfrentarse al mayor rival al que jamás se haya enfrenado, Mortimer Drake, mientras Green Arrow se encuentra con un nuevo enemigo.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: Hogar, Dulce Hogar
added.description: Los Fantásticos vuelven a casa y se dan cuenta de que el tiempo no ha pasado. Pronto descubren que su conocimiento acerca de las batallas ha aumentado de forma exponencial.

added.title: Un Golpe de Ternura
added.description: Después de derrotar a Strata, Los Fantásticos se dan cuenta de que no volvieron solos, sino con un Bakugan parecido a un panda que les dará muchos problemas.

added.title: El Hijo Prodigo
added.description: Mientras los Fantásticos intentan evolucionar a sus Bakugan como lo hizo Dan con Drago, el primo de Shun, Masato, llega a la ciudad para llevarlo de regreso a Japón.

added.title: El Poder Interior
added.description: Masato Kazami vuelve junto con los guardaespaldas de la familia para llevar a Shun a Japón, pero esta vez, Shun y Hydorous tienen una sorpresa preparada.

added.title: El Baul de los Recuerdos
added.description: Al ser confrontada por China Riot, Lia logra evolucionar a Pegatrix cuando comprende la verdadera razón de su obsesión por las cámaras.

added.title: Malos Actores
added.description: Alguien expone a Dan por mentir acerca de la evolución de Drago, mientras el equipo se enfrenta a Duran Dane y su desdichado Bakugan, Nillious.

added.title: El Atrapador
added.description: Dan y Wynton se encuentran con la posible ubicación secreta de la Célula Núcleo, y con el coronel Tripp, que busca apoderarse de la fuente de energía.

added.title: La Sed de Poder
added.description: Tras una discusión entre Wynton y Dan, el coronel Tripp controla la mente de Wynton para que ataque la ciudad con Lupitheon. Esto inicia una guerra entre Los Fantásticos y el ejército.

added.title: Un Triunfo Robado
added.description: Dan se embarca en una aventura para superar al nuevo equipo de Peleadores Bakugan de Magnus, pero al final, ellos lo salvarán a él.

added.title: La Aventura de Lightning
added.description: Lightning descubre la Célula Núcleo enterrada bajo tierra, y se enfrenta a Strata El Cazador para intentar proteger su secreto.

added.title: El Oso Troyano
added.description: Cuando Axel abre una caja de regalo de suscripción que ni siquiera ordenó, el equipo encuentra sus filas divididas por un oso robótico, io la Princesa SugarSalt disfrazada!

added.title: Que Comience la Fiesta
added.description: Mientras Zoe prepara la fiesta de cumpleaños de Cleo LeBall, Axel y el equipo controlan los daños contra una estrelladora celosa: ila princesa SugarSalt, que ha convertido las decoraciones y los regalos en instrumentos de caos!

added.title: Criando Bebe
added.description: Zoe deja a Axel a cargo del proyecto escolar, vigilando una muñeca simulador de bebés, pero cuando MadCap da vida a la muñeca, iAxel y el equipo deben detener al bebé sin dañarlo o correr el riesgo de obtener una calificación reprobatoria!

added.title: Estirado Demasiado Delgado
added.description: Después de que un nuevo movimiento combinado deja a Masko permanentemente flácido, Axel y el equipo deben ayudar al luchador caído a recuperarse.

added.title: #GatoCallejero Parte 2
added.description: Cuando Zee Zatara se da cuenta de que Lex Luthor desenterró un libro mágico que tiene el poder de predecir el futuro, las chicas le piden ayuda a Gatúbela para robárselo antes de que Lex comprenda lo que tiene en su poder. Pero puede que ya sea demasiado tarde...
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: Sed de Poder
added.description: Axel y sus juguetes despliegan el Joyride en una batalla de "barco" a "barco" contra el Dr. Nautilus, quien ha perforado una tubería de agua para inundar las alcantarillas y se ha establecido como "Almirante Nautilus".

added.title: #GatoCallejero Parte 1
added.description: Cuando Zee Zatara se da cuenta de que Lex Luthor desenterró un libro mágico que tiene el poder de predecir el futuro, las chicas le piden ayuda a Gatúbela para robárselo antes de que Lex comprenda lo que tiene en su poder. Pero puede que ya sea demasiado tarde...
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol
